divs: Sighting DetailsI was filming in my back yard what I thought was a black contrail and caught something else. Pointing WSW about 4:30 pm dusk, 12-24-2009. It was difficult to get the camera to focus because it was so cold outside and that seems to cause problems with the focus on the camera. I didn't actually realize I had caught anything else until I was loading it up on my computer. I didn't think it was normal for a plane to maneuver in front of another plane this way.
